---
/**
 * CachingStrategies.astro
 * When to cache, patterns for effective prompt caching
 * Pure CSS, dark theme
 */
---

<div class="cs-wrap">
  <h3 class="cs-title">When Prompt Caching Pays Off</h3>
  
  <div class="cs-grid">
    <div class="cs-card cs-good" style="--i:0;">
      <div class="cs-label">✅ Great ROI</div>
      <div class="cs-items">
        <div class="cs-item">RAG systems with large static context</div>
        <div class="cs-item">Multi-turn conversations with system prompts</div>
        <div class="cs-item">Batch processing with same instructions</div>
        <div class="cs-item">Agents with long tool/function schemas</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cs-card cs-bad" style="--i:1;">
      <div class="cs-label">❌ Low ROI</div>
      <div class="cs-items">
        <div class="cs-item">Short prompts under 1,024 tokens</div>
        <div class="cs-item">Unique one-off queries</div>
        <div class="cs-item">Rapidly changing context each request</div>
        <div class="cs-item">Low request volume (cache expires)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="cs-tip">
    <div class="cs-tip-label">💡 Key Insight</div>
    <div class="cs-tip-text">Structure prompts with stable content first (system prompt, tools, context docs) and variable content last (user query). Caching matches from the prefix — anything after the first difference is a miss.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .cs-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  .cs-title {
    color: #f1f5f9;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .cs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .cs-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .cs-card {
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: csFade 0.5s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: calc(var(--i) * 0.2s);
  }
  @keyframes csFade {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .cs-good {
    background: rgba(74,222,128,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.25);
  }
  .cs-bad {
    background: rgba(239,68,68,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.25);
  }
  .cs-label {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .cs-good .cs-label { color: #4ade80; }
  .cs-bad .cs-label { color: #ef4444; }
  .cs-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .cs-item {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .cs-item::before {
    content: '•';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #64748b;
  }
  .cs-tip {
    background: rgba(245,158,11,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: csFade 0.5s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
  }
  .cs-tip-label {
    color: #f59e0b;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .cs-tip-text {
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
